snippet.title: Assassin's Creed Codename Hexe Official Announcement Trailer | Ubisoft Forward 2022
snippet.description:
Following Baghdad and Japan, the mainline Assassin's Creed series seems to be going to the Holy Roman Empire during the witch trials, in a game described by executive producer Marc-Alexis Côté as "a very different type of Assassin's Creed game."

#assassinscreed #ubisoftforward #gaming
